{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "label": "Minhas Obras (piv\u00f4 do dashboard financeiro)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "App pivota de finan\u00e7as pessoais para controle de custos de obras de alto padr\u00e3o. Sucesso = usu\u00e1rio (pai do Giovani, construtor) entende em 5 segundos quanto gastou em cada obra e, ao vender, v\u00ea se bateu o banco. Mant\u00e9m identidade visual dark premium aprovada, login local e PWA offline-first; app.js reescrito do zero."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_valor_corrigido", "label": "Valor corrigido (custo de oportunidade)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Juro composto pr\u00f3-rata por dia: corrigido = valor \u00d7 (1+taxa)^(dias/30.44), da data do gasto at\u00e9 hoje ou at\u00e9 a venda (congela). Taxa \u00fanica global (padr\u00e3o 1% a.m.); mudar a taxa recalcula tudo \u2014 sem hist\u00f3rico de taxas de prop\u00f3sito, para a conta ser transparente e confer\u00edvel. Exemplo can\u00f4nico: 10.000 \u2192 ~10.615 em 6 meses."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_fases_da_obra", "label": "Fases da Obra (constru\u00e7\u00e3o / pronta / vendida)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Toda fase pode voltar atr\u00e1s (marcou errado). Obra pronta continua aceitando gastos (IPTU, manuten\u00e7\u00e3o); obra vendida n\u00e3o aceita gastos novos e congela a corre\u00e7\u00e3o na data da venda."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_modelo_de_dados_obra", "label": "Modelo de dados Obra/Config (blob por usu\u00e1rio)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Obra { id, nome, fase, dataInicio, valorEstimadoVenda?, venda?, gastos[] } + Config { taxaMensal=0.01, topicosCustom[] }, originalmente em localStorage por usu\u00e1rio."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_topicos_padrao", "label": "T\u00f3picos de gasto padr\u00e3o (14)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Terreno inclu\u00eddo de prop\u00f3sito: \u00e9 o maior gasto t\u00edpico e entra na corre\u00e7\u00e3o desde o dia 1. Usu\u00e1rio pode criar t\u00f3picos pr\u00f3prios; remo\u00e7\u00e3o s\u00f3 se o t\u00f3pico n\u00e3o tiver gastos."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_simulador_vender_agora_vs_depois", "label": "Simulador vender agora vs. depois (Vale a pena?)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Taxa composta mensal equivalente do lucro ((venda/custo)^(1/meses) \u2212 1) comparada com a taxa do banco; se venda > custo corrigido, bateu o banco. Deixado fora de escopo no piv\u00f4, mas a estrutura de dados j\u00e1 comporta."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_valor_corrigido", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_fases_da_obra", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_modelo_de_dados_obra", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_topicos_padrao", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_minhas_obras", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_simulador_vender_agora_vs_depois", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_simulador_vender_agora_vs_depois", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_valor_corrigido", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_valor_corrigido", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_modelo_de_dados_obra", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.95, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": [{"id": "padrao_bruto_vs_corrigido", "label": "Padr\u00e3o bruto \u00d7 corrigido pelo banco em toda a UI", "nodes": ["docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_04_obras_design_valor_corrigido", "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_grafico_evolucao_da_obra", "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_relatorio_simulador_design_relatorio_da_simulacao", "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_kpis_na_obra_design_kpis_da_obra"], "relation": "participate_in", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-04-obras-design.md"}]}